('GeneralHouseBrothersChristianSchoolsRome', '<p class=\"justify\">Casa Generalizia dei Fratelli delle Scuole Cristiane<br>Via Aurelia, 476<br><br>The remains of Saint John Baptist de la Salle (d. 1719) were transferred here in 1937. They now rest in the sanctuary of the church.<br><br>During the early 18th century he founded a community of consecrated laymen commonly referred to as the Christian Brothers. This community pioneered many educational reforms within France.</p>', '', '', '', '', ''),
